data.title: Drowsy Chaperone - Vocal Selections
data.meta_description: Drowsy Chaperone - Vocal Selections Ten songs from the hilarious Broadway musical that won the most 2006 Tonys, plus the New York Critics' Circle and Drama Desk awards for Best Musical. Includes: Accident Waiting to Happen Bride's Lament Cold Feets I Am Aldolpho I Remember Love Show Off Toledo Surprise and more.
data.text: Drowsy Chaperone - Vocal Selections Ten songs from the hilarious Broadway musical that won the most 2006 Tonys, plus the New York Critics' Circle and Drama Desk awards for Best Musical. Includes: Accident Waiting to Happen • Bride's Lament • Cold Feets • I Am Aldolpho • I Remember Love • Show Off • Toledo Surprise • and more.
